Enhancement: Allow end-of-line comments in files read via `--files-from`

`restic-backup` now supports end-of-line comments in files provided via the
`--files-from` option. As an example:

```
/path/to/foo.bar # this comment is ignored
```

https://github.com/restic/restic/issues/3705
https://github.com/restic/restic/pull/3706
